https://cookiecutter.readthedocs.io/

install
-------

    $ pip install cookiecutter

usage
-----

- grab a cookiecutter template

    $ git clone git@github.com:audreyr/cookiecutter-pypackage.git

- personalize your copy: modify variables in cookiecutter.json, change skeleton project and push to your own cookiecutter repo if need be for future reuse.

- generate your project from the project template

    # with directories 
    $ cookiecutter cookiecutter-pypackage/


    # with repos
    $ cookiecutter https://github.com/audreyr/cookiecutter-pypackage
    # also works with abbreviations for github (gh), bitbucket (bb), and gitlab (gl)
    $ cookiecutter gh:audreyr/cookiecutter-pypackage

    # with zip files 
    $ cookiecutter /path/to/template.zip

configuration
-------------
- templates are downloaded to ~/.cookiecutter
- replay json files are under ~/.cookiecutter_replay


replaying after failed execution
--------------------------------

    $ cookiecutter --replay <template name>

    # e.g.
    $ cookiecutter --replay cookiecutter-django
